A menacing troll creature in traditional folklore style crouching beneath a gleaming modern suspension bridge in a tropical harbor at dusk, clutching a tangled web of glowing fiber optic cables in its gnarled claws, the Singapore skyline visible in the misty background with its distinctive skyscrapers, the troll's eyes gleaming with cunning greed as ships pass underneath, warm orange sunset reflecting off the water contrasting with the cold blue glow of the stolen cables, Studio Ghibli animation style with rich watercolor textures, expressive character design, and atmospheric lighting creating both whimsy and unease
